description: Hunky Diego Sans and athletic Pierre Fitch are on a first date enjoying each other’s company. Hairy Diego is already horny, and ready to taste a piece of adorable Pierre, but Pierre doesn’t want to give it up just yet. He heads home feeling like he might have missed out on a good experience. His roommate urges him to call Diego back after trying a Pure for men capsule. Muscular Diego is more than happy to hear from tattooed Pierre, and invites him over so they can end their date properly.
title: Bottoms Up
